{
  "text": "The objective function J is minimized by using, for instance, stochastic gradient descent. The term (A \u00b7 A T \u2212 I) F is introduced to penalize the choice of the same weights for each attention hops in matrix A (see [CITATION_1] ).",
  "correct_citation": {
